text: Benedikt Nikpalj (; born 6 September 1993) is a Croatian bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Croatia Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
